description: This file defines data classes related to move results in a 2048 puzzle game, including classes for individual move steps, merge steps, spawned tiles, and the aggregate move result object.

classes.name: MoveStep
classes.description: Represents a single tile movement from one position to another.

classes.name: MergeStep
classes.description: Represents the merging of two tiles into a new tile with a specified value at a given position.

classes.name: SpawnInfo
classes.description: Represents a newly spawned tile with its position and value.

classes.name: MoveResult
classes.description: Encapsulates the complete outcome of a move, including steps, merges, spawns, score, and game state flags.

methods.name: MoveResult.empty
methods.description: Creates an empty move result indicating no changes, with flags for winning or game over state.
